::: Ominous sees Zerling coming, and over hearing the comm message sent out, 
he wasnt happy. If Zardus thought he was such a threat, he would show him 
just how dangerous he was :::

::: Ominous Prime waited until Zerling was in range, he then sprung out and 
wrapped his hands around Zerlings neck and began to suck out his energy. :::

~~~~~~~~

::: Hell Beast ::: For the love of.....Alright, bring up shields and 
Auto-guns! Prepare to engage!

::: Pheniox and Balck Aracnia's hands jetted over the keyboards setting up 
the Shield and Auto-guns. With a sound of thunder, Hell Beast, Gremlin, 
Jackle, Marine, and Transanulas burst out of the Base and into the cross fire 
:::

~~~~~~~~`

::: Set watched as an invisible like spider web covered the ship, dozens of 
battered auto-guns popped up, and a small fighting force of the Predacons 
rushed out of the Base led by Hell Beast. :::
